<TEXT>
<P>
Sizzling Ticket Price for 'Miss Saigon': "Miss Saigon" promises to be a 
megaproduction when it opens at the Broadway Theater in New York next March. 
</P>
<P>
There'll be a helicopter landing on stage, a huge statue of Ho Chi Minh . . . 
and extra high ticket prices. The top ticket price for the best seats will be 
$100. Compare that to highest price at the Los Angeles Music Center Opera, $75; 
the top ticket (unscalped) for L.A "Phantom of the Opera," $50. BETH KLEID 
