RIGHTS; ENVIRONMENTALISTS; VENTURA COUNTY -- DEVELOPMENT AND REDEVELOPMENT; LOS 
ANGELES COUNTY -- DEVELOPMENT AND REDEVELOPMENT; NATIONAL PARK SERVICE; NATURE 
RESERVES; PARKS -- CALIFORNIA; LAND USE; PROPERTY SALES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
