<P>
SUPREME COURT (U.S.) -- RULINGS; DEATH ROW; CAPITAL PUNISHMENT; COURT REFORM; 
UNITED STATES -- COURTS; APPEALS; TRENDS; CIVIL RIGHTS VIOLATIONS; PRISONERS 
RIGHTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
