ANGELES COUNTY -- POLITICS; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- DEVELOPMENT AND 
REDEVELOPMENT; REAPPORTIONMENT -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; RACIAL DISCRIMINATION; 
HISPANICS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; VOTING RIGHTS; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- HISTORY 
