to finish first in the Big East. ; Photo, Israeli-born Nadav Henefeld has gone 
from the Middle East to the Big East with Connecticut. ; Photo, COLOR, (San 
Diego Edition) Like everyone else, Connecticut Coach Jim Calhoun didn't expect 
Huskies to finish first in the Big East. MICHAEL McANDREWS / Hartford Courant 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
