<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The New York Rangers acquired high-scoring right wing Mike Gartner from the 
Minnesota North Stars for Ulf Dahlen, also a right wing. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
