now in doubt. Last week, Gannett said it would no longer finance GTG after 
March 31. The independent producer employs about 250 people, of which 160 are 
associated with the "Baywatch" series on NBC. A spokesman said Tinker has two 
pilot commitments at CBS and expressed confidence that a backer could be found 
if CBS decided to order the shows for next season. 
</P>
