pitch, and scored on an error to break a 9-9 tie in the seventh for host Los 
Alamitos (1-1-1). Anthony Napolitano had a double, triple and four RBIs for Los 
Alamitos. 
</P>
<P>
Irvine 9, Downey 5 -- Host Irvine (1-2) had only six hits but Downey made five 
errors leading to five unearned runs. Bobby Ray pitched five innings for the 
victory. 
</P>
<P>
Dana Hills 15, Riverside North 8 -- Todd Futa had three doubles and four RBIs 
for host Dana Hills (2-1). Mark Spurlock had two hits including a three-run 
